# Corpus protection (2026-05-19): rth-expand branch has 3,150 corpus dates
# main does not. Without this rule, a checkout of rth-expand into the working
# tree shows those dates as untracked, and `git add` sweeps them in (PR #799
# mishap). Tracked dates already in main keep tracking — gitignore only
# affects untracked files. Corpus untracked wholesale on staging on 2026-05-20.
data/20*/
